WEBVTT

01:29:48.441 --> 01:29:49.649
And the theatre staff.

01:29:49.816 --> 01:29:51.191
All my relatives
must be invited in person.

01:29:51.233 --> 01:29:52.899
-That's not necessary.
-Huh?

01:29:52.941 --> 01:29:54.399
Just call everyone
over the phone.

01:29:54.441 --> 01:29:55.941
And send the invite on WhatsApp.

01:29:55.983 --> 01:29:57.149
Dad!
